{"tid":1398774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花］今期流行 罷工Challenge","createTime":"2019-08-03T02:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:20:12.000Z","uid":18577,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe2ac38596702dbe6b562f631e43b1a25226575","tid":1398774,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"我諗大家都好記得幾年前facebook hit到爆嘅冰桶challenge<br />\n<br />\n今次我哋香港人就發起一個罷工challenge..實行要勁過上之冰桶challenge <br />\n<br />\n黎一真真正正嘅香港人CHALLENGE <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做法如下：<br />\n由開post起計，參加者要係自己fb/ig貼一張圖，表明自己會參與當中<br />\n<br />\n參加者完成挑戰嘅同時，另可最多tag 3人要求佢哋效仿依個行為<br />\n<br />\n被點名者需於48小時內，接受「挑戰」或向任何同反送中有關團體（如612基金/星火/立場新聞等）捐款<br />\n<br />\n二選一或你兩樣做哂就當然最歡迎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLXJ6gV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLXJ6gV.png&h=db70c8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太多野想寫<br />\n寫到密麻麻<br />\n<br />\n#今期流行 罷工Challenge <br />\n#8月5日 全港三罷<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#你今日罷咗未<br />\n#你唔係唔罷呀嘛"},{"pid":"cfd85b996890401594edc1ae95d7e0b919dec788","tid":1398774,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"今期流行<br />\n罷工Challenge <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9fa3f078cfa2f17739bdd19618c91a6b83c177","tid":1398774,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bf7557da9d3ce250e4f635f3e636da3ba53e44","tid":1398774,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237575f3678fd8733aec9054ad6d0623a21afd26","tid":1398774,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201